  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0db8\u0d9c\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0db1\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Basil's departure is stopped due to the protest of the passengers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Finance Minister Basil Rajapaksa left his flight early this morning (12th) due to a protest from passengers inside the Katunayake airport when he left for the United States via Dubai.",
        "Katunayake Airport duty manager also confirmed this. Mr. Basil Rajapaksa has arrived at the Katunayake airport to board Emirates flight EK-349, which is scheduled to depart for Dubai at 03.15 this morning.",
        "There, the air passengers who were standing near the Emirates and Sri Lankan Airlines inspection windows near the \"Silk Route\" shouted that Mr. Basil Rajapaksa should be removed from the airport and he left the airport."
      ],
